# RQ-53-10-01-025: AOA Sensor Mounting

## Requirement Statement
The nose cone shall provide mounting provisions for 3 angle-of-attack (AOA) vanes.

## Acceptance Criteria
- 3 AOA vane locations on nose sides
- 500mm minimum separation
- Heated vanes (anti-ice)
- Position in undisturbed airflow

## Compliance Status
Design complete, flight test validation planned

## Traceability
Parent: ATA 34 (Air Data System)
